      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I'm honestly so excited to show you this absolute gem. It\u2019s in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered its whole life, and you won\u2019t find a single scratch or dent anywhere. It drives like a dream and still has that fresh new-car smell. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. Come take it for a spin, you\u2019re going to love it! \u2728",
