    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant. This specimen boasts a comprehensive service history, including documented rod bearing replacement and proactive subframe reinforcement. The 3.2L straight-six breathes through individual throttle bodies, providing exceptional volumetric efficiency and razor-sharp throttle response. Power is delivered via a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis remains taut with refreshed bushings and original dampers, maintaining its legendary handling characteristics. With flawless paint depth and a pristine cabin, this is a turnkey investment for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
