      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of exceptional caliber, maintained in impeccable, showroom-grade condition. This specimen exhibits no discernible wear, reflecting a rigorous standard of preservation that will satisfy the most discerning automotive enthusiast. From the flawless exterior luster to the pristine interior appointments, every detail confirms its status as a premier example of the marque. We invite serious inquiries to acquire a vehicle that transcends the standard pre-owned market in both presentation and mechanical integrity.",
